{"arkId":"cl010099352","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099352","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Tabati\u00e8re","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tabati\u00e8re"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Antiquit\u00e9 ; \u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime (Occident)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1740 - 1760","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 614 - Galerie Louis XV, Vitrine 17","room":"Salle 614, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1740,"endYear":1760,"imprecision":"vers","text":"Milieu du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6761","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Tabati\u00e8re de jaspe sanguin taill\u00e9 \u00e0 cuvette. Elle est de forme rectangulaire avec une b\u00e2te en balustre. Son d\u00e9cor est sculpt\u00e9 en l\u00e9ger bas-relief sur le couvercle, on y trouve un chasseur et une chasseresse entour\u00e9s de trois chiens, sur un fond de paysage. Cette sc\u00e8ne est encadr\u00e9e de rocailles avec des incrustations de petits dimants taill\u00e9s en brillant ou en rose. La bordure est cisel\u00e9e d\u0027ondes. \r\nSur la b\u00e2te : quatre sc\u00e8nes de chasse avec un ampur ail\u00e9. L\u0027une au cerf ; l\u0027une au lion ; la torisi\u00e8me \u00e0 l\u0027ours et la derni\u00e8re au loup. \r\nSur le bec : incrustation d\u0027un rubis de Birmanie taill\u00e9 \u00e0 facettes et de dimanats dont deux sont taill\u00e9s en brillants. \r\nLa gorge est en or, l\u0027int\u00e9rieur de la tabati\u00e8re est en or d\u00e9coup\u00e9 de festons sur la bordure.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ;  (Sans poin\u00e7ons)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,5","displayDimension":"3,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"7,8","displayDimension":"7,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"6","displayDimension":"6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : jaspe\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nMat\u00e9riau : diamant","placeOfCreation":"Allemagne (Europe) ((?))","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection baron Basile de Schlichting (1857-1914) Paris. Legs 1914","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Baron Schlichting, Basile de","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1914","startYear":1914,"endYear":1914}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs"}],"period":[{"value":"Antiquit\u00e9"},{"value":"\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime"}],"place":[{"value":"Allemagne"}],"objectType":[{"value":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Grandjean, Serge, Catalogue des tabati\u00e8res boites et \u00e9tuis des XVIIIe et XIXe si\u00e8cles du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, [Collections du Mus\u00e9e du Louvre], Paris, RMN, 1981","bibliographyDate":"1981","bibliographyDetail":"p. 301, n\u00b0 458","comp